Farm_bot.changelog:
Changes in Farm_bot:
- Added a random nickname change option.
- It will change immediately upon launch and before teleportation (if activated).

Universal.changelog:
Changes in Universal:
- Added the 'Only hell event' parameter 
- If this option is enabled, the account will only participate in hellish events, then close the game until the next event.

Hunt.changelog:

- There was a problem with hunting spots (there weren't enough of them in k13 XD).
- Added about 15 spots (about 30 in total).
- We will test whether the new spots will interfere with each other when hunting.
- Bugs fixed.
